MERRY CHRISTMAS FROM SAN DIEGO!
We’re alive. Haven’t been very active on here due the move. After driving 24 hours in 28 hours, we made it to the new home in San Diego. The past few months have been chaos. Buying a house, shipping holiday orders, packing/moving an art studio, shipping room and personal belongings across the country have all been exhausting. Mentally and physically drained but so grateful and excited about the future! My store inventory is set to arrive Jan 14th and I’ll reopen the shop once it’s here. Hope y’all have a great holiday season! 
Also, SD locals, 👋, let’s get coffee soon.

First time drawing in a month. First drawing in San Diego. Feeling rusty but glad to be back at it. Swipe to see other half. Thanks for looking!

TATTOOS?
Some answers for my most common DM… 
• If you would like to use an existing piece of my art for your tattoo design, go for it!  • Please give proper credit if a photo is posted online. Example: Original artwork by @samlarson. 
• It’s always rad to see a photo if you do get something tattooed of mine! 
• I don't allow tattoo artists to make flash sheets of my designs. 
• I’m currently not taking on any custom tattoo designs unless we are friends.
• Ways to support me for the use of the artwork... Purchasing something on my store or sending a tip via Venmo @SteelBison. Thank You!!!

#tattoos #tattoo

Just finished this custom for @tomdelonge. New guitar for the upcoming @blink182 tour. This is the only custom art I’ve taken on the past year. Forever grateful what he has done for me and couldn’t be happier to be a part of this!
